134
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:59,840
The horrific tricks of simple Lissa don't work once you are vaccinated.

135
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,640
And the vaccine is special for another reason.

136
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,200
Because Lissa is so slow in the first few weeks,

137
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,520
